{"type":null,"faqId":20033,"title":"为什么我的 HUAWEI MediaPad T1 8.0 Pro 不能设置日期和时间？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>这可能是由于您已经选择了使用网络上的时间， HUAWEI MediaPad T1 8.0 Pro 将直接获取网络时间，而无需手动设置。如需手动设置时间，请参考如下步骤：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕上点击“设置 &gt; 日期和时间”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>清除“自动确定日期和时间”后的复选框。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"figd0e3369\"><a name=\"gen-id1.11.9.2.2.2.2.1\"></a></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=66809\" style=\"width:2.6625in;height:3.9375in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>根据界面提示，手动设置日期、时间等信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<a name=\"gen-id1.11.9.2.3\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=66810\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":175,"faqType":"系统功能及设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3454","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1425286529000,"seriesProductName":"T1-821w,T1-823L","visitedTimes":61,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"日期,时间,设置日期,设置时间","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}